snippet.title: Mother Tensei: F3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for the upcoming EarthBound ROM hack, "Mother Tensei." The hack will be a combination of EarthBound and Shin Megami Tensei elements, both in gameplay and story.

You can learn more about the project and follow it's development here: https://forum.starmen.net/forum/Community/PKHack/M-o-t-h-e-r-T-e-n-s-e-i

Twitter:
